Variables-
Variables are used to store and manage data. It is like a container that holds data.
Variables name must start with letter or underscore character.
Variables name cannot start with number.
Varibles name can only contain alphanumeric character and underscore


Example 
Assigning multiple variables to many values
a,b,c = "Mango","Orange","Banana"
print(a)
print(b)
print(c)
